title: HomePortal 3801HGV Gateway User Guide
description:
HomePortal 3801HGV Gateway User Guide:

The HomePortal 3801HGV Gateway Installation and Configuration Guide is designed to serve as a reference to install and set up the HomePortal 3801HGV gateway.  This is the 2-Wire VDSL Home Portal Gateway router used by AT&T for their uverse service.

It has all the setup info you might want (or need) to be able to configure your router differently from what the technician did when installing.

Hope it helps you as it did me.
